                        <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><DIV><FONT size=2 face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif>(North Carolina, Southern Secession, and&nbsp;Civil War: Northern&nbsp;(Union)
                           pictorial envelope published during the&nbsp;Civil War showing the Devil holding the North Carolina state seal and&nbsp;the
