                        </p>
                        <div><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><DIV align=center><STRONG><FONT size=4>North Carolina in the&nbsp;American Civil War:&nbsp;Overview</FONT></STRONG>
                           <!--"''"--></DIV></font>
                        </div>
                        <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="black"><b><i><script type="text/javascript"><!--
                           google_ad_client = "ca-pub-2111954512596717";
