                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif"><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="1" color="black"><b><i>North Carolina Civil War Battlefields and Battles</i></b></font></td>
                                 </tr>
