                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif" width="560"><font face="Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="1" color="black"><b><i>Vital North Carolina Civil War Railroads Map</i></b></font></td>
                                 </tr>
