                           War Sources: </FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Walter Clark, Histories of the Several
                           Regiments and Battalions from North Carolina in the Great War 1861-1865;&nbsp;<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black;
