                           of History; State Library of North Carolina; North Carolina Department of Agriculture; University Library, The University
                           of North Carolina at Chapel Hill; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:
