                           Library of Congress; <SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Official Records of the Union and Confederate
                           Armies;&nbsp;</SPAN>National Archives and Records Administration;&nbsp;United States Department of Veterans Affairs; Library
                           of Congress: American War Casualty Lists and Statistics; William F. Fox, Regimental Losses in the American Civil War; Gettysburg
                           National Military Park.</SPAN></SPAN></P></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT>
                           <!--"''"--></DIV></font>
                        </p>
                        <!--/area Type="subhead"-->
                     </td>
                  </tr>
